{"tid":1958537,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無龍槍（Dragonlance）系列小說迷 ?","createTime":"2020-04-04T17:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T12:08:03.000Z","uid":69994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce85b4cf0011580d02107474ef85bbb532925066","tid":1958537,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:38:06.000Z","msg":"暫時係好讀網睇左呢幾套主線小說<br />\n【修瑪傳奇】<br />\n【龍槍編年史三部曲】<br />\n【龍槍傳奇三部曲】<br />\n【雷斯林傳奇二部曲】<br />\n【龍槍傳承】<br />\n【夏焰之巨龍】<br />\n【靈魂之戰三部曲】<br />\n<br />\n魔戒 (LOTR) 有睇電影 , 除左哈比人(同咕嚕) , 其他角色都好平坦 ...<br />\n睇完龍槍小說對比下 , 完全感嘆龍槍系列點解無一套影視作品 !<br />\n團隊角色個個有血有肉 , 世界觀龐大 , 發展起黎不會在 STARWARS 或者 MARVEL 之下 .<br />\n而且主線跨越幾十年 , 大部分主角都有變老 (精靈除外) , 加入後輩角色 , 拍攝影視的話唔會出現續集主角太老唔連戲或者做唔返動作戲既情況 !<br />\n雷斯林 (Raistlin) 既角色描寫最細緻有魅力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 泰斯 (Tasslehoff) 同埋侏儒既情節都係我睇小說讀過最好笑最好笑既 , 沒有之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上搵到既美系風格插畫真係唔靚 , 可能係年代久遠關係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYGx8Zj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYGx8Zj.jpg&h=71a883ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQBY4xE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQBY4xE.jpg&h=cade9fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCykyqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCykyqY.jpg&h=7ac413d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot; 萬色返空龍 &quot; 個名好型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&quot; 施拉克 (Shirak) ! &quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3b0b38813ae0801d74624a990e52758296741f","tid":1958537,"uid":187355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:45:31.000Z","msg":"修瑪/夏炎/傳承有中文版？"},{"pid":"de65ab24387629b8d90b4723149b503950310dc0","tid"